The paper deals with source coding with side information, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). It also discusses multi-user source coding, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). The use of side information is a common theme in signal processing (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the trade-off between rate and distortion, which is a fundamental concept in data science (cs.DS). Finally, the paper uses mathematical optimization techniques to derive the optimal solutions, which is a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG).
